00:33:08,820 --> 00:33:10,339
Keluarlah dari sana sekarang.

458
00:33:10,363 --> 00:33:12,603
<i>Jalanlah ke lorong,
pasti ada panel logistik.</i>

459
00:33:12,782 --> 00:33:14,677
Jika kau tunjukkan, aku bisa
pandu kalian harus ke mana.

460
00:33:14,701 --> 00:33:16,721
<i>Bawa anak - anak.
Jangan matikan telepon.</i>

461
00:33:16,745 --> 00:33:18,031
<i>Baik.</i>

462
00:33:19,998 --> 00:33:22,240
Berikan handuknya.
Ayo.

463
00:33:22,334 --> 00:33:24,872
<i>Peringatan hunian
di lantai 98.</i>

464
00:33:29,674 --> 00:33:32,633
Keluarga Will Sawyer membuka
pintu apartemen sejam yang lalu.

465
00:33:32,719 --> 00:33:35,302
Mereka masih di dalam.
Kirim dua orang.

466
00:33:35,931 --> 00:33:38,423
Gunakan kode manual di lift.

467
00:33:38,517 --> 00:33:40,509
Bawa mereka ke sini.
/ Baik, Pak.

468
00:33:40,602 --> 00:33:41,763
Kalian berdua, cepat.

469
00:33:43,396 --> 00:33:45,716
Apa ? Apinya takkan padam.

470
00:33:46,024 --> 00:33:47,265
Kita harus pergi sekarang.

471
00:33:48,401 --> 00:33:52,145
<i>Peringatan keamanan.</i>
FASILITAS SISTEM KENDALI

472
00:33:58,870 --> 00:34:00,657
Aku hanya bisa dapat
kendali sedikit.

473
00:34:01,206 --> 00:34:03,286
Aku tak bisa
dapat kendali tanpa...

474
00:34:05,919 --> 00:34:06,919
...akses root.

475
00:34:07,587 --> 00:34:08,623
Baik.

476
00:34:25,564 --> 00:34:26,680
Kami sudah masuk.

477
00:34:27,580 --> 00:34:28,780
IZIN ADMIN TIDAK VALID

478
00:34:29,480 --> 00:34:30,480
AKSES DITOLAK

479
00:34:31,778 --> 00:34:33,565
Seluruh sistem
telah diretas.

480
00:34:33,655 --> 00:34:35,317
Aku benar  -benar terkunci.

481
00:34:35,949 --> 00:34:37,176
Apa maksudmu kau terkunci ?

482
00:34:37,200 --> 00:34:38,532
Kukira itu tak bisa terjadi.

483
00:34:38,618 --> 00:34:41,138
<i>Kita dapat kendali penuh</i>
<i>sistem anti kebakaran.</i>

484
00:34:42,122 --> 00:34:44,865
Tutup semua pintu anti api
dari lantai 95 ke bawah.

485
00:34:45,166 --> 00:34:48,204
<i>Dan matikan sistem anti
kebakaran lantai 96 ke atas.</i>

486
00:35:03,101 --> 00:35:04,412
<i>Semua akan baik saja.</i>

487
00:35:04,436 --> 00:35:06,268
<i>Panel logistik
harusnya di kirimu.</i>

488
00:35:08,106 --> 00:35:09,666
<i>Katakan yang kau lihat.</i>

489
00:35:10,108 --> 00:35:11,108
Baik, sayang.

490
00:35:12,193 --> 00:35:13,553
Semua lantai atas
berwarna kuning.

491
00:35:13,653 --> 00:35:15,715
Apa artinya ?
/ Artinya sistem anti kebakaran...

492
00:35:15,739 --> 00:35:16,739
...di atasmu mati.

493
00:35:17,032 --> 00:35:18,989
<i>Sarah, dengar.
Apinya takkan mati.</i>

494
00:35:19,576 --> 00:35:21,576
Keluar dari sana sekarang dan naik.

495
00:35:21,661 --> 00:35:23,903
Terus naik, jangan berhenti.
Jangan lihat ke belakang.

496
00:35:23,997 --> 00:35:25,600
<i>Sekarang paksa
apinya ke atas.</i>

497
00:35:25,624 --> 00:35:26,809
<i>Buka ventilasi udara
dari lubang lift...</i>

498
00:35:26,833 --> 00:35:29,416
<i>...dan beri oksigen segar.</i>

499
00:35:30,337 --> 00:35:31,794
Biarkan terbakar.

500
00:35:32,339 --> 00:35:33,455
Hadirin.

501
00:35:34,341 --> 00:35:36,128
Kupersembahkan...

502
00:35:36,217 --> 00:35:38,049
...cerobong asap
6,5 miliar dolar.

503
00:35:48,688 --> 00:35:50,304
Ny. Sawyer ?

504
00:35:50,857 --> 00:35:52,137
Kami keamanan gedung.

505
00:35:52,192 --> 00:35:53,192
Tolong ikut kami.

506
00:35:56,196 --> 00:35:57,437
Tidak ! Mundur !
/ Lari !

507
00:36:02,911 --> 00:36:04,948
Tidak ! Tidak !

508
00:36:15,298 --> 00:36:17,631
Bagaimana keadaan kalian ?
Melaporlah.

509
00:36:20,053 --> 00:36:21,134
Kalian dengar ?

510
00:36:22,806 --> 00:36:24,593
Tak ada yang bisa selamat
dari itu. Mereka sudah mati.

511
00:36:25,350 --> 00:36:27,710
<i>Kami bergerak ke posisi.</i>
Kau tahu harus apa.

512
00:36:29,729 --> 00:36:31,649
<i>Cepat, naik tangga.
/ Sarah.</i>

513
00:36:33,149 --> 00:36:34,149
BURON

514
00:36:34,275 --> 00:36:35,607
Will Sawyer.

515
00:36:42,280 --> 00:36:44,077
<font color=#ffff00>Angkat tangan !</font>

516
00:36:47,205 --> 00:36:48,662
Kumohon.
Kalian tak paham.

517
00:36:48,748 --> 00:36:51,161
Keluargaku di dalam.
Dengarkan aku.

518
00:36:51,251 --> 00:36:52,458
Aku harus jemput mereka.
/ Berbalik !

519
00:36:54,499 --> 00:36:56,311
<font color=#ffff00>Sekarang !</font>

520
00:37:21,838 --> 00:37:23,838
PENGENAL WAJAH DIMATIKAN

521
00:37:24,784 --> 00:37:27,777
Kau punya akses penuh
ke sistem dari tablet.

522
00:37:28,288 --> 00:37:29,728
Tak perlu pengenal wajah.

523
00:37:29,789 --> 00:37:32,873
Semua akses komputer utama
The Pearl telah dienkripsi.

524
00:37:33,418 --> 00:37:35,910
Sekarang seluruh
gedung terkunci.

525
00:37:36,379 --> 00:37:38,587
Kugunakan kode logaritma
milikku untuk meretasnya.

526
00:37:38,673 --> 00:37:42,041
Jadi, hanya aku di Bumi
yang bisa memecahkan ini.

527
00:37:43,595 --> 00:37:44,802
Cerdas sekali, 'kan ?

528
00:37:47,265 --> 00:37:48,847
Tak terlalu cerdas.

529
00:37:48,933 --> 00:37:50,469
Jika api terus naik...,

530
00:37:50,560 --> 00:37:52,426
...udara di sekitar helipad
akan sangat panas...

531
00:37:52,520 --> 00:37:53,852
...membuat tak bisa terbang.

532
00:37:53,938 --> 00:37:55,520
Waktu keberangkatan
hampir habis, Pak.

533
00:37:56,524 --> 00:37:58,231
Sekarang atau tidak sama sekali.

534
00:37:58,318 --> 00:37:59,879
<i>Peringatan. Sistem
anti kebakaran mati.</i>

535
00:37:59,903 --> 00:38:02,236
Senang ?
Kau bisa jadi pahlawan...

536
00:38:02,322 --> 00:38:03,858
...tapi gagal.
Saatnya pergi.

537
00:38:04,824 --> 00:38:07,441
Keinginanmu terkabul,
Tn. Pierce.

538
00:38:08,203 --> 00:38:09,489
Siapkan landasan.

539
00:38:10,622 --> 00:38:11,829
Siapkan helikopter.

540
00:39:23,553 --> 00:39:25,381
<font color=#ffff00>Will Sawyer itu siapa ?</font>

541
00:39:26,382 --> 00:39:28,088
<font color=#ffff00>Angkatan Laut,
Bintang Perunggu...,</font>

542
00:39:28,089 --> 00:39:32,285
<font color=#ffff00>...6 tahun di FBI dan 8 tahun
di Tim Penyelamat Sandera.</font>

543
00:39:32,286 --> 00:39:34,041
<font color=#ffff00>Punya seorang istri
dan dua anak.</font>

544
00:39:34,042 --> 00:39:35,516
<font color=#ffff00>Istrinya ahli bedah militer.</font>

545
00:39:35,517 --> 00:39:37,343
<font color=#ffff00>Istrinya tiga kali bertugas
di Afghanistan.</font>

546
00:39:37,344 --> 00:39:39,814
<font color=#ffff00>Lokasinya belum diketahui.</font>

547
00:39:39,815 --> 00:39:42,848
<font color=#ffff00>Will Sawyer direkrut
jadi konsultan keamanan.</font>

548
00:39:42,849 --> 00:39:46,959
<font color=#ffff00>Dia punya akses
protokol keamanan gedung.</font>

549
00:39:47,479 --> 00:39:51,243
<font color=#ffff00>Hanya dia yang bisa
mematikan sistem anti kebakaran.</font>

550
00:39:51,507 --> 00:39:54,381
<font color=#ffff00>Cari Will Sawyer.</font>

551
00:39:54,382 --> 00:39:56,316
<font color=#ffff00>Aku ada pertanyaan.</font>

552
00:39:56,840 --> 00:39:57,972
<font color=#ffff00>Baik, Pak.</font>

553
00:39:58,409 --> 00:39:59,934
<font color=#ffff00>Sersan Han.</font>

554
00:40:00,435 --> 00:40:02,787
<font color=#ffff00>Aku menemukannya.</font>

555
00:40:05,904 --> 00:40:08,068
<font color=#ffff00>Astaga.</font>

556
00:40:19,413 --> 00:40:21,162
<font color=#ffff00>Kirim tim respons.</font>

557
00:40:21,163 --> 00:40:22,249
<font color=#ffff00>Aku ingin menanyainya.</font>

558
00:40:22,767 --> 00:40:24,634
<font color=#ffff00>Baik, Pak.</font>

559
00:40:41,900 --> 00:40:44,500
<font color=#ffff00>Lift-nya terkunci !
Cepat !</font>

560
00:40:45,323 --> 00:40:47,423
Sial.

561
00:40:54,331 --> 00:40:56,463
<font color=#ffff00>Dia sedang apa ?</font>

562
00:40:56,464 --> 00:40:58,566
<font color=#ffff00>Dia naik ke arah kebakaran.</font>

563
00:43:26,354 --> 00:43:30,064
Pak, aku tak bisa melindungimu
jika ada yang kau rahasiakan.

564
00:43:30,775 --> 00:43:32,937
Ini bukan kebakaran biasa.
Ini jebakan.

565
00:43:33,486 --> 00:43:36,229
Aku masih tak yakin.
/ Tak perlu.

566
00:43:36,864 --> 00:43:39,402
Menurutmu siapa pelakunya ?

567
00:43:40,034 --> 00:43:41,241
Kores Botha.

568
00:43:43,162 --> 00:43:44,494
Aku tak paham.

569
00:43:45,414 --> 00:43:48,452
Jika Botha ingin membunuhmu,
ada cara yang lebih mudah.

570
00:43:48,543 --> 00:43:52,537
Dia tak ingin membunuhku.
Belum saatnya.

571
00:43:53,840 --> 00:43:55,297
Dia ingin ini.

572
00:43:56,008 --> 00:43:58,408
Membakar The Pearl
satu-satunya cara mendapatkannya.

573
00:44:00,388 --> 00:44:01,845
Ada sesuatu
yang harus kutahu ?

574
00:44:02,348 --> 00:44:05,341
Ya.
Helikopter sudah siap.

575
00:44:23,265 --> 00:44:24,765
PANJANG MAKSIMUM

576
00:44:30,614 --> 00:44:31,714
PENGAIT

577
00:45:02,038 --> 00:45:05,182
<font color=#ffff00>Dia mencoba masuk.</font>

578
00:45:14,086 --> 00:45:15,327
Maaf, Teman-teman.

579
00:45:44,242 --> 00:45:45,733
Sial.

580
00:45:49,914 --> 00:45:50,914
Maju !

581
00:45:52,743 --> 00:45:54,143
<font color=#ffff00>Jangan bergerak !</font>

582
00:45:54,168 --> 00:45:56,251
Angkat tangan !
/ Baik. Jangan tembak.

583
00:45:56,275 --> 00:45:58,129
<font color=#ffff00>Berbalik !</font>

584
00:45:58,130 --> 00:45:59,399
Berbalik.

585
00:46:15,200 --> 00:46:16,600
<font color=#ffff00>Tahan tembakan !</font>

586
00:46:30,524 --> 00:46:31,771
<font color=#ffff00>Terlalu panas !</font>

587
00:46:31,772 --> 00:46:33,320
<font color=#ffff00>Ketinggian berkurang !</font>

588
00:46:57,898 --> 00:46:59,139
Ya!

589
00:47:06,863 --> 00:47:10,004
<font color=#ffff00>Apa yang membuatnya
ingin menerobos masuk ?</font>

590
00:47:10,212 --> 00:47:11,375
<font color=#ffff00>Inspektur...</font>

591
00:47:11,376 --> 00:47:15,104
<font color=#ffff00>Kami mendapat lokasi terakhir
keluarga Will Sawyer.</font>

592
00:47:15,108 --> 00:47:16,799
<font color=#ffff00>Biar kutebak.</font>

593
00:47:16,800 --> 00:47:18,710
<font color=#ffff00>Mereka di dalam gedung.</font>

594
00:47:20,755 --> 00:47:22,212
Lewat sini.

595
00:47:24,592 --> 00:47:27,175
Bagus. Tunggu.
Kemari.

596
00:47:27,970 --> 00:47:30,210
Basahi ini lagi, paham ?
/ Paham, Bu.

597
00:47:31,515 --> 00:47:34,508
Baik. Tenanglah.

598
00:47:34,602 --> 00:47:36,844
Sebentar.

599
00:47:36,937 --> 00:47:38,457
Suara apa itu ?

600
00:47:38,481 --> 00:47:39,847
Suara api, Sayang.

601
00:47:42,443 --> 00:47:43,479
Kita mau ke mana ?

602
00:47:43,569 --> 00:47:44,650
Entah.

603
00:47:45,363 --> 00:47:48,026
Itu jembatan menuju air terjun.
Kita terus naik.

604
00:47:51,035 --> 00:47:52,035
Lari !

605
00:48:00,336 --> 00:48:01,456
Naik tangga.

606
00:48:04,256 --> 00:48:05,497
Terus lari.

607
00:48:06,675 --> 00:48:07,961
Jangan berhenti.

608
00:48:09,145 --> 00:48:11,445
<font color=#ffff00>Helikopter siap lepas landas.</font>

609
00:48:12,425 --> 00:48:15,225
PINTU DIBUKA

610
00:48:38,499 --> 00:48:39,499
Tunggu.

611
00:48:40,418 --> 00:48:41,499
Ada apa ?

612
00:48:44,296 --> 00:48:46,253
Itu bukan pilot kita.
/ Botha.

613
00:48:47,716 --> 00:48:48,716
Merunduk !

614
00:48:55,141 --> 00:48:56,141
Lari !

615
00:49:18,330 --> 00:49:19,787
Lama tak berjumpa, Botha.

616
00:49:19,874 --> 00:49:21,706
Ya. Rindu aku ?

617
00:49:22,585 --> 00:49:24,121
Kau sudah bertemu rekanku.

618
00:49:24,670 --> 00:49:26,036
Kejutan.

619
00:49:27,381 --> 00:49:28,963
Mengapa tak bunuh aku
dan mengambilnya ?

620
00:49:30,217 --> 00:49:31,628
Pikirmu aku bodoh ?

621
00:49:32,136 --> 00:49:33,377
Aku tak bisa.

622
00:49:33,471 --> 00:49:34,951
Karena bosku
akan membunuhku...

623
00:49:35,014 --> 00:49:37,472
...jika barangnya tak sampai.

624
00:49:37,558 --> 00:49:40,551
Mestinya kau bayar aku
dan masalah selesai, tapi tidak.

625
00:49:40,644 --> 00:49:42,684
Kau selalu sok pintar.

626
00:49:44,273 --> 00:49:45,684
Bagaimana kalau begini ?

627
00:49:46,817 --> 00:49:49,776
Aku akan membawamu,
pilotmu...,

628
00:49:49,862 --> 00:49:50,862
...dan helikoptermu.

629
00:49:51,280 --> 00:49:55,069
Kau akan melihat
gedungmu habis terbakar...

630
00:49:55,159 --> 00:49:56,719
...dan tak bisa
berbuat apa-apa.

631
00:50:06,712 --> 00:50:08,044
Awas !

632
00:50:38,141 --> 00:50:40,641
PINTU DITUTUP

633
00:50:44,750 --> 00:50:45,750
Zhao !

634
00:50:49,255 --> 00:50:50,291
Zhao !

635
00:50:56,595 --> 00:50:57,595
Ya.

636
00:50:59,515 --> 00:51:02,553
Dia mengunci griya tawang.
Buka pintunya.

637
00:51:05,187 --> 00:51:08,187
Lantai griya tawang
punya subrutin sendiri.

638
00:51:08,190 --> 00:51:09,977
Zhao mengisolasi sistemnya.

639
00:51:10,818 --> 00:51:12,775
Tablet ini tak bisa
membuka pintunya.

640
00:51:13,362 --> 00:51:16,662
Tunggu. Will Sawyer
ada di gedung.

641
00:51:16,782 --> 00:51:18,364
Ada alarm pergerakan.

642
00:51:19,201 --> 00:51:20,567
Itu keluarganya.

643
00:51:21,161 --> 00:51:22,402
<i>Mereka masih hidup.</i>

644
00:51:23,497 --> 00:51:24,908
Zhao !

645
00:51:46,979 --> 00:51:48,720
Tak bisa masuk pakai otot.

646
00:51:49,607 --> 00:51:51,644
Kau butuh orang
yang tahu sistemnya.

647
00:51:52,693 --> 00:51:54,935
Aku tahu orangnya.

648
00:51:55,863 --> 00:51:57,070
Sawyer.

649
00:51:57,573 --> 00:51:59,656
Hanya dia yang bisa masuk.

650
00:51:59,742 --> 00:52:02,359
Dia di gedung.
Kita tinggal mencarinya.

651
00:52:04,288 --> 00:52:05,950
Tak perlu mencarinya.

652
00:52:06,999 --> 00:52:08,615
Kita tahu keinginannya.

653
00:52:56,090 --> 00:52:57,547
Jika tak bisa diperbaiki
dengan lakban...,

654
00:53:00,511 --> 00:53:01,991
...maka lakbannya
kurang banyak.

655
00:53:24,322 --> 00:53:25,522
MODE ADMIN

656
00:53:25,577 --> 00:53:29,036
Kalian di lantai 98,
tangga sisi timur.

657
00:53:30,082 --> 00:53:31,882
Artinya kalian
harus lewat taman.

658
00:53:32,584 --> 00:53:33,870
Aku akan cari kalian.

659
00:53:34,253 --> 00:53:35,585
Sabarlah.

660
00:53:54,606 --> 00:53:57,349
Tetap sadar, Sayang.

661
00:53:57,443 --> 00:53:59,059
Hampir sampai.

662
00:54:10,247 --> 00:54:12,847
Ny. Sawyer.
/ Ya.

663
00:54:13,751 --> 00:54:14,867
Senang bertemu denganmu.

664
00:54:16,962 --> 00:54:18,373
Ketemu.
Mereka di taman.

665
00:54:18,881 --> 00:54:20,213
Ayo.

666
00:54:20,299 --> 00:54:22,507
Anak-anak juga.
/ Lakukan perintahnya.

667
00:54:22,843 --> 00:54:25,426
Benar.
Dengarkan ibu kalian.

668
00:54:25,846 --> 00:54:28,930
Tenang.
Semua akan baik saja.

669
00:54:29,516 --> 00:54:30,757
Lakukan perintah Ibu.

670
00:54:31,810 --> 00:54:33,551
Lari !

671
00:54:36,815 --> 00:54:38,306
Ibu !
/ Ayo !

672
00:55:08,764 --> 00:55:10,426
Ayo.

673
00:55:10,516 --> 00:55:12,098
Naik sedikit lagi.

674
00:55:20,567 --> 00:55:21,808
Georgia !

675
00:55:22,361 --> 00:55:23,568
Henry !

676
00:55:24,822 --> 00:55:26,313
Aku cari jalan lain.

677
00:55:26,406 --> 00:55:28,568
Naiklah ke air terjun.

678
00:55:28,659 --> 00:55:30,275
Aku ke sisi lain.

679
00:55:30,369 --> 00:55:32,531
Kita bertemu di sana.
/ Baiklah.

680
00:55:43,465 --> 00:55:45,172
Aku tak perlu membunuhmu.

681
00:55:45,259 --> 00:55:47,592
Cukup anak-anakmu saja.

682
00:55:47,678 --> 00:55:48,794
Sarah !

683
00:55:56,061 --> 00:55:57,677
Kau tak apa ?
/ Ya.

684
00:56:00,649 --> 00:56:01,981
Bagaimana caramu
masuk gedung ?

685
00:56:02,067 --> 00:56:03,808
Ceritanya panjang.
Mana anak-anak ?

686
00:56:03,902 --> 00:56:05,985
Ayah ! Ibu !
/ Kau tak apa ?

687
00:56:06,071 --> 00:56:07,983
Jangan bergerak.
